32struct _gss_mechanism_name {
33 HEIM_SLIST_ENTRY(_gss_mechanism_name) gmn_link;
34 gssapi_mech_interface gmn_mech; /* mechanism ops for MN */
35 gss_OID gmn_mech_oid; /* mechanism oid for MN */
36 gss_name_t gmn_name; /* underlying MN */
37};
38HEIM_SLIST_HEAD(_gss_mechanism_name_list, _gss_mechanism_name);
39
40struct _gss_name {
41 gss_OID_desc gn_type; /* type of name */
42 gss_buffer_desc gn_value; /* value (as imported) */
43 struct _gss_mechanism_name_list gn_mn; /* list of MNs */
44};
45
46OM_uint32
47 _gss_find_mn(OM_uint32 *, struct _gss_name *, gss_OID,
48 struct _gss_mechanism_name **);
49struct _gss_name *
50 _gss_make_name(gssapi_mech_interface m, gss_name_t new_mn);
